WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:06.700
Mom, why are you here?

2
00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:08.000
Rice noodles, come here.

3
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.233
Mom wants to talk to you

4
00:00:11.900 --> 00:00:13.533
Mom, what's the matter?

5
00:00:13.533 --> 00:00:14.700
It's the following.

6
00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:17.500
Your dad suddenly feels sorry for you

7
00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:20.233
I want to take you back to the Dong family to make up for you

8
00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:23.000
He hates me so much.

9
00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:24.966
I feel like I should be humiliated exclusively

10
00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:26.566
Kill my mother-in-law

11
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:27.866
Take my son

12
00:00:28.100 --> 00:00:30.333
He will feel sorry for me

13
00:00:30.333 --> 00:00:31.566
And he's old now.

14
00:00:31.566 --> 00:00:33.266
Mom also persuaded him a lot

15
00:00:33.266 --> 00:00:34.866
He knew it was wrong.

16
00:00:34.866 --> 00:00:36.366
It's family after all.

17
00:00:36.366 --> 00:00:37.766
Blood is thicker than water

18
00:00:37.766 --> 00:00:39.666
Just forgive him

19
00:00:40.466 --> 00:00:43.100
But my husband must not have died in vain

20
00:00:43.300 --> 00:00:45.300
Mom misses you every day

21
00:00:45.300 --> 00:00:47.466
Now I have a chance to miss you

22
00:00:47.466 --> 00:00:50.000
Don't you even want your mother?

23
00:00:51.700 --> 00:00:55.300
Mom, I'm going back

24
00:01:04.066 --> 00:01:04.866
Mom

25
00:01:06.933 --> 00:01:09.233
What, come to grandma's house later?

26
00:01:10.566 --> 00:01:11.433
OK

27
00:01:25.333 --> 00:01:28.766
What are you doing here with the owner?

